title: Microsoft Azure Virtual Network Gateways: BGP
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check shows settings and peering addresses of a Microsoft
 Azure virtual network gateway's BGP.

 In order to use this check, you need to configure the Azure special agent.

item:
 The name of the resource.

discovery:
 One service is created for each virtual network gateway.
